---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="About — Chitti" description="Learn about Chitti's mission — AI beauty specialists, skin analysis, and personalized routines in one private, emotionally safe companion.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-bg-mint via-bg-cream to-bg-blush py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-text sm:text-5xl">
        A beauty companion that
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-light to-primary-dark bg-clip-text text-transparent">truly knows you</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-light">
        Chitti brings together AI skincare, haircare, and makeup specialists with deep skin analysis, smart routines, and progress tracking — all in one private, emotionally safe companion.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="bg-white py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
      <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            We created Chitti because beauty advice is broken. Generic tips. Expensive dermatologist visits for basic questions. Products pushed by influencers who've never seen your skin. We wanted something that actually knows you — your skin, your products, your routines — and gives advice that's genuinely personal.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            Chitti is a complete beauty platform with dedicated AI specialists for skincare, haircare, and makeup. It analyzes your skin, tracks your products, builds your routines, runs structured product trials, and monitors your progress over time — all from one companion that remembers everything about you.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text">What We Believe</h2>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-4">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 flex h-6 w-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary">
                <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              </span>
              <span class="text-text-light"><strong class="text-text">Privacy first.</strong> Your photos are encrypted, never used for AI training, and never shared with advertisers. You control your data — delete everything from the app at any time.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 flex h-6 w-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary">
                <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              </span>
              <span class="text-text-light"><strong class="text-text">Kindness always.</strong> Feedback that starts with your strengths, not your flaws.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 flex h-6 w-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary">
                <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              </span>
              <span class="text-text-light"><strong class="text-text">Culturally aware.</strong> Beauty is local. Chitti understands regional context and cultural nuance.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 flex h-6 w-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary">
                <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              </span>
              <span class="text-text-light"><strong class="text-text">Truly personal.</strong> Every conversation knows your skin analysis, products, and routines — so advice is never generic.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Cultural Context -->
  <section class="bg-bg-cream py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text">Built for the world, tuned for you</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed text-text-light">
        Chitti adapts to your cultural context. Whether you're in Mumbai preparing for a traditional celebration or in New York getting ready for a night out, Chitti understands the nuances that matter to you.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="mb-4 text-3xl">🇮🇳</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text">India</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-light">
            Understands traditional and modern Indian beauty sensibilities, regional preferences, and cultural celebrations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="mb-4 text-3xl">🌍</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text">Western</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-light">
            Detail-oriented feedback with emphasis on trends, technique, and evidence-based skincare recommendations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</PageLayout>
